connected to Emily?

01:15:47.175 --> 01:15:48.809
Kell?

01:15:48.811 --> 01:15:50.845
Yeah, I'm here.

01:15:50.847 --> 01:15:51.679
I don't know.

01:15:51.681 --> 01:15:52.313
Maybe.

01:15:52.315 --> 01:15:53.347
